  <data key="d10">Insulin-dependent but ketosis-resistant diabetes</data>
  <data key="d11">Ketosis-resistant diabetes is a synonym for type II diabetes. This term thus refers to a form of type II diabetes in which patients are dependent on insulin.</data>
